      <title>一旦基准利率接近 3% 欧洲央行降息将变得更加棘手</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/ecb-cuts-to-get-trickier-once-key-interest-rate-approaches-3</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，一旦利率降至 3% 左右，欧洲央行的决策将变得更加激烈，围绕如何控制通胀出现分歧也将加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/ecb-cuts-to-get-trickier-once-key-interest-rate-approaches-3</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
