    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Pimco 预计日本央行最早将于 1 月加息，看好长期日本国债</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/pimco-sees-boj-hike-as-soon-as-january-likes-long-term-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[太平洋投资管理公司日本分公司预计央行最早将于明年 1 月再次加息，并准备积极投资超长期政府债券，这些债券的收益率已升至更具吸引力的水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/pimco-sees-boj-hike-as-soon-as-january-likes-long-term-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 01:47:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
